214
00:16:02.230 --> 00:16:05.030
I thought you were dead...

215
00:16:05.360 --> 00:16:07.780
Well, Kid?

216
00:16:09.530 --> 00:16:10.780
You scum!

217
00:16:10.780 --> 00:16:11.990
Queen!

218
00:16:11.990 --> 00:16:14.700
They're running wild!

219
00:16:16.000 --> 00:16:19.460
How are we supposed
to catch them alive like this?!

220
00:16:21.080 --> 00:16:22.710
Who said you couldn't kill 'em?

221
00:16:30.890 --> 00:16:32.390
Repel!

222
00:16:38.020 --> 00:16:40.560
Anyone with a death wish, step right up!

223
00:16:41.060 --> 00:16:43.320
I'll be your executioner!

224
00:16:47.070 --> 00:16:48.200
There he is!

225
00:16:48.200 --> 00:16:49.910
I knew Killer would be here too!

226
00:17:05.170 --> 00:17:07.840
Kid! Let's get out of here!

227
00:17:09.590 --> 00:17:12.300
There's nothing to gain
from fighting them here!

228
00:17:13.010 --> 00:17:14.930
I guess you've got a point...

229
00:17:21.770 --> 00:17:23.440
Hey, stop!

230
00:17:23.440 --> 00:17:26.530
Even if you kill them,
you can't be part of the Soaring Six!

231
00:17:41.710 --> 00:17:42.870
Whoa, whoa, quit it!

232
00:17:42.870 --> 00:17:44.040
You'll hurt us, too!

233
00:17:53.390 --> 00:17:54.970
Get out of here!

234
00:17:56.220 --> 00:17:58.890
Somebody, stop him!

235
00:18:00.230 --> 00:18:02.690
I guess that's my cue...

236
00:18:02.690 --> 00:18:04.480
Time to scram!

237
00:18:05.110 --> 00:18:08.480
Seems like they can't control
that guy! But who is he?!

238
00:18:09.070 --> 00:18:12.400
A giant? No, he's way too big!

239
00:18:26.750 --> 00:18:30.170
Haccha
One of the Numbers

240
00:18:30.170 --> 00:18:31.840
Attaboy, Haccha!

241
00:18:42.350 --> 00:18:45.730
Looks like I'll be taking Kid's head!

242
00:18:58.410 --> 00:19:00.740
Jaggy! Let's make a dash for the castle!

243
00:19:11.130 --> 00:19:12.380
Man...

244
00:19:12.800 --> 00:19:16.300
I knew you'd start something, Jaggy!

245
00:19:16.300 --> 00:19:19.010
Look who's talking, Luffy!

246
00:19:19.930 --> 00:19:21.640
You're just as bad, Roronoa!

247
00:19:22.850 --> 00:19:24.520
They're all hopeless.

248
00:19:26.270 --> 00:19:28.310
Yay!

249
00:19:28.310 --> 00:19:33.610
Once I break out my battle
music, there's no escape!

250
00:19:33.610 --> 00:19:35.150
Here we go!

251
00:19:35.150 --> 00:19:37.320
Encore! Check it out!

252
00:19:38.160 --> 00:19:40.740
Hey! Cover your ears!

253
00:19:40.740 --> 00:19:41.910
Check it out!

254
00:19:41.910 --> 00:19:43.790
Boom!

255
