264
00:20:08.730 --> 00:20:10.020
Listen up, guys!

265
00:20:11.020 --> 00:20:12.770
Apoo attacks using sound itself!

266
00:20:12.770 --> 00:20:16.740
If you can hear the attack,
it's already too late to dodge!

267
00:20:17.200 --> 00:20:18.700
So keep an eye on him!

268
00:20:20.530 --> 00:20:21.240
– What?
– What?

269
00:20:22.410 --> 00:20:25.790
Since it's so important,
I'll say it one more time!

270
00:20:25.790 --> 00:20:26.620
Okay!

271
00:20:31.290 --> 00:20:33.750
They finally contacted me!

272
00:20:33.750 --> 00:20:38.050
They said the ship was fine,
so they should be here soon!

273
00:20:38.050 --> 00:20:39.380
How curious...

274
00:20:39.380 --> 00:20:41.970
Are you sure, Big Mom?

275
00:20:42.760 --> 00:20:47.140
There's been no word of new
arrivals from Mogura Port...

276
00:20:48.730 --> 00:20:50.270
Port?

277
00:20:50.730 --> 00:20:52.690
There's a port?

278
00:20:53.270 --> 00:20:54.650
Huh...?!

